headline: Cardinal Health to Announce Second-Quarter Results for Fiscal Year 2026 on February 5
summary: Cardinal Health (NYSE: CAH) plans to release second-quarter financial results for its fiscal year 2026 on February 5, prior to the opening of trading on the New York Stock Exchange. The company will webcast a discussion of these results beginning at 8:30 a.m. Eastern.
